lead_paragraph: Australian flanker Dean Mumm is available for Saturday's Twickenham showdown with England after being cleared of a red-card offence during last weekend's defeat by Ireland, World Rugby (WR) said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Australia's Mumm Cleared to Face England
